      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·邶風·009.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">aou-y ew-koo-y eh •.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>匏有苦葉，濟有深涉，深則厲，淺則揭。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The gourd has [still] its bitter leaves,
And the crossing at the ford is deep.
If deep, I will go through with my clothes on;
If shallow, I will do so, holding them up.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__guofeng-beifeng-009__002__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sheking-1871-ocr">
      <prop type="x-work-id">shijing</prop>
