      <prop type="x-alignment-granularity">stanza</prop>
      <prop type="x-is-coarse-alignment">false</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">0.99</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·邶風·009.2</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">aou-y ew-koo-y eh •.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>有瀰濟盈，有鷕雉鳴，濟盈不濡軓，雉鳴求其牡。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The ford is full to overflowing;
There is the note of the female pheasant.
The full ford will not wet the axle of my carriage;
It is the pheasant calling for her mate.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__guofeng-beifeng-009__003__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sheking-1871-ocr">
