      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·邶風·009.4</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">aou-y ew-koo-y eh •.4</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>招招舟子，人涉卬否，人涉卬否，卬須我友。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The boatman keeps beckoning;
And others cross with him, but I do not.
Others cross with him, but I do not; —
I am waiting for my friend.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
